\emph on

\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

J'étudie math ou micro.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 
\emph default
et 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset


\emph on
Je n'étudie pas math.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout
Le syllogisme disjonctif donne donc: 
\emph on

\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

J'étudie micro.
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_inset


